{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Debt_is_Incurred",
  "title": "A Debt is Incurred",
  "summary": "Bruised and weary, Venus enters the Imperial Embassy lobby once more to request a meeting with Vice Director Thistleborne, expecting the usual refusal. There she catches the eye of Director Joir, the Royal Guard who once served as her protector during her time as Alaric's slave, and the years of unspoken understanding between them resurface instantly. Reading her fatigue and the fading bruises on her face, Joir approaches and quietly demands to know who hurt her; Venus reluctantly names Claudio Van Eyre, a cruel business associate who already owes Joir a debt. With cold conviction Joir vows that the man will never harm her again, and the two retire to a private conference chamber where their guarded intimacy deepens, Venus reaffirming her Imperial blood through her late grandfather Lord Dekan and Joir betraying both tenderness and lingering disapproval of her former allegiances.",
